209
0:08:13.26,000 --> 0:08:15,000
The energy of empty space

210
0:08:15.26,000 --> 0:08:17,000
brings to life quantum fluctuations.

211
0:08:17.26,000 --> 0:08:19,000
And so even though the universe will last forever,

212
0:08:19.26,000 --> 0:08:22,000
and ordinary matter and radiation will dilute away,

213
0:08:22.26,000 --> 0:08:24,000
there will always be some radiation,

214
0:08:24.26,000 --> 0:08:26,000
some thermal fluctuations,

215
0:08:26.26,000 --> 0:08:28,000
even in empty space.

216
0:08:28.26,000 --> 0:08:3,000
So what this means

217
0:08:30.26,000 --> 0:08:32,000
is that the universe is like a box of gas

218
0:08:32.26,000 --> 0:08:34,000
