229
0:09:00.26,000 --> 0:09:02,000
It's very, very unlikely.

230
0:09:02.26,000 --> 0:09:04,000
Except if they locked the doors

231
0:09:04.26,000 --> 0:09:06,000
and kept us here literally forever,

232
0:09:06.26,000 --> 0:09:08,000
that would happen.

